    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i'm hearing some people say that these lessons are basically \"essential\" for kids to be kind to each other and that anyone against it is just being closed-minded. but then i have friends who say it's actually harmful to kids. do you think there's any truth to the idea that these programs are just a way to push a specific agenda rather than just being about \"inclusivity\"?",
